The '''''Watcher''''' was an [[Imperial Customs Frigate]] under the command of the [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|Imperial Star Destroyer]] ''[[Revenge]]''. It once took the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Starship/Legends|ship]] ''[[Arion Star]]'' on board for inspection, but allowed it depart when no contraband was found on board.

